cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR 

This paper deals with the task of generating descriptive captions for satellite images using machine learning models. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves natural language processing and machine learning, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses the size and deployment of models, which could place it in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) sub-categories.
